context:
KR:
&lt;워더링하이츠는 왜 떠나오게 된 거야? 좋아하는 사람이 있었던 곳인데.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Why’d you leave Wuthering Heights? It's where the love of your life lives, isn't it?&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;말해줄래? 왜 워더링하이츠를 떠나지 않고서는 견딜 수가 없었는지.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;Tell me. Tell me why you couldn't bear to remain at Wuthering Heights anymore.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;하지만… 지금은?&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;But... what about now?&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;그렇다면… 네가 할 수 있는 건, 뭐가 있을까?&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;Then... what can you do now?&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;넌 저 모습을 보면 어떤 생각이 들어?&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;Look at him. What do you feel?&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;히스클리프. 너는 너를 어떻게 생각해?&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;What do you think of yourself, Heathcliff?&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;주인에게 버려진 울부짖으며 날뛰는 슬픈 사냥개…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;A wild, heartbroken hound, abandoned by his master...&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;그게 지금 너만의 마음이고, 되고 싶은 모습이구나.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;... that is the shape of your heart and its desire, isn't it?&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;너의 바람대로 될 수 있어.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#dc3531&gt;Then it can be as you wish.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;집으로 온 걸 환영해, 히스클리프.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;Welcome home, Heathcliff.&lt;/color&gt;
